《'''鴿子與豌豆'''》（'''''Le pigeon aux petit pois'''''<ref name="bbc">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/europe/10130840.stm |title=Five masterpieces stolen from Paris modern art museum |date=20 May 2010 |newspaper=[[BBC_News_Online|BBC News Online]] |accessdate=2013-12-15 |archive-date=2012-06-30 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120630115956/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/europe/10130840.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>）是[[巴勃羅·畢加索|巴勃羅·畢加索]]在1911年完成的畫作。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/news/la-fg-paintings-stolen-pictures,0,4090079.photogallery |title=PHOTOS: Theft at Paris Museum of Modern Art |accessdate=20 May 2010 |date=20 May 2010 |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |publisher=[[Tribune_Company|Tribune Company]] |archive-date=2010-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100522123059/http://www.latimes.com/news/la-fg-paintings-stolen-pictures,0,4090079.photogallery |dead-url=no }}</ref> 是2010年5月20日[[巴黎現代藝術博物館|巴黎現代藝術博物館]]被盜的五幅作品之一，這些畫作的總價值為1.23億美元。

次年盜賊和主使者被發現，但是並沒有找到失竊作品。<ref>{{Citation|author=Nathaniel Herzberg|newspaper=Le Monde|date=2012-05-15|title=A la recherche du butin perdu}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://newsfeed.time.com/2012/04/16/pilfered-paintings-five-famous-art-heists-through-history/slide/good-artists-borrow-great-artists-steal/ |title=Time Magazine, May 2012 |accessdate=2013-12-15 |archive-date=2019-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191227051906/http://newsfeed.time.com/2012/04/16/pilfered-paintings-five-famous-art-heists-through-history/slide/good-artists-borrow-great-artists-steal/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

